@page "/about"

<PageTitle>About</PageTitle>

<div class="w-full px-5 md:px-50 py-12 text-slate-80 overflow-y-auto">
  <h1 class="mb-6 text-3xl font-light">About JsonUI</h1>

  <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">
    <strong>JsonUI</strong> is a browser-based developer tool for converting JSON
    data structures into strongly typed source code.
  </p>

  <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">
    The site is intended for software developers who work with APIs and other
    forms of structured data.
  </p>

  <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">
    JsonUI is an independent project developed and maintained by an independent developer.
  </p>

  <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">
    The project was created to reduce repetitive boilerplate code and make working
    with JSON data easier and more predictable.
  </p>

  <p class="leading-relaxed">
    For questions or feedback, you can contact us at
    <a href="mailto:json.ui.se@gmail.com" class="text-blue-600 underline hover:text-blue-800">
      json.ui.se@gmail.com
    </a>.
  </p>
</div>